searchData={"items":[{"type":"module","title":"opentelemetry_nova","doc":"","ref":"opentelemetry_nova.html"},{"type":"function","title":"opentelemetry_nova.setup/0","doc":"","ref":"opentelemetry_nova.html#setup/0"},{"type":"function","title":"opentelemetry_nova.setup/1","doc":"","ref":"opentelemetry_nova.html#setup/1"},{"type":"module","title":"otel_nova_plugin","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_plugin.html"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_plugin.plugin_info/0","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_plugin.html#plugin_info/0"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_plugin.post_request/4","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_plugin.html#post_request/4"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_plugin.pre_request/4","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_plugin.html#pre_request/4"},{"type":"module","title":"otel_nova_prom_exporter","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.html"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.export/4","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.html#export/4"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.force_flush/0","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.html#force_flush/0"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.get_metrics/0","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.html#get_metrics/0"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.init/1","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.html#init/1"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.shutdown/0","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_exporter.html#shutdown/0"},{"type":"module","title":"otel_nova_prom_handler","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_handler.html"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_handler.init/2","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_handler.html#init/2"},{"type":"module","title":"otel_nova_prom_server","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_server.html"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_server.handle_call/3","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_server.html#handle_call/3"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_server.handle_cast/2","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_server.html#handle_cast/2"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_server.handle_info/2","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_server.html#handle_info/2"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_server.init/1","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_server.html#init/1"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_server.start_link/1","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_server.html#start_link/1"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_server.stop/0","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_server.html#stop/0"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_prom_server.terminate/2","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_prom_server.html#terminate/2"},{"type":"module","title":"otel_nova_stream_h","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_stream_h.html"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_stream_h.data/4","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_stream_h.html#data/4"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_stream_h.early_error/5","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_stream_h.html#early_error/5"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_stream_h.info/3","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_stream_h.html#info/3"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_stream_h.init/3","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_stream_h.html#init/3"},{"type":"function","title":"otel_nova_stream_h.terminate/3","doc":"","ref":"otel_nova_stream_h.html#terminate/3"},{"type":"extras","title":"opentelemetry_nova","doc":"# opentelemetry_nova\n\nOpenTelemetry instrumentation for the [Nova](https://github.com/novaframework/nova) web framework.\n\nAutomatic HTTP request tracing and metrics with Prometheus export support.","ref":"readme.html"},{"type":"extras","title":"Installation - opentelemetry_nova","doc":"Add to your dependencies in `rebar.config`:\n\n```erlang\n{deps, [\n    {opentelemetry_nova, \"~> 0.1\"}\n]}.\n```","ref":"readme.html#installation"},{"type":"extras","title":"Setup - opentelemetry_nova","doc":"Call `setup/0` during application startup:\n\n```erlang\nopentelemetry_nova:setup().\n```\n\nOr with Prometheus export:\n\n```erlang\nopentelemetry_nova:setup(#{prometheus => #{port => 9464}}).\n```","ref":"readme.html#setup"},{"type":"extras","title":"Metrics - opentelemetry_nova","doc":"The following metrics are collected automatically:\n\n| Metric | Type | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| `http.server.request.duration` | Histogram (seconds) | Request duration |\n| `http.server.active_requests` | UpDown Counter | Currently active requests |\n| `http.server.request.body.size` | Histogram (bytes) | Request body size |\n| `http.server.response.body.size` | Histogram (bytes) | Response body size |","ref":"readme.html#metrics"},{"type":"extras","title":"Components - opentelemetry_nova","doc":"- **`otel_nova_stream_h`** - Cowboy stream handler for HTTP tracing and metrics\n- **`otel_nova_plugin`** - Nova plugin for span enrichment with controller/action attributes\n- **`otel_nova_prom_exporter`** - Prometheus exporter with delta-to-cumulative conversion\n- **`otel_nova_prom_server`** - HTTP server for Prometheus scraping","ref":"readme.html#components"},{"type":"extras","title":"License - opentelemetry_nova","doc":"Apache 2.0","ref":"readme.html#license"},{"type":"extras","title":"LICENSE","doc":"MIT License\n\nCopyright (c) 2019 Daniel Widgren\n\nPermission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy\nof this software and associated documentation files (the \"Software\"), to deal\nin the Software without restriction, including without limitation the rights\nto use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, and/or sell\ncopies of the Software, and to permit persons to whom the Software is\nfurnished to do so, subject to the following conditions:\n\nThe above copyright notice and this permission notice shall be included in all\ncopies or substantial portions of the Software.\n\nTHE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED \"AS IS\", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR\nIMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO THE WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY,\nFITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE AND NONINFRINGEMENT. IN NO EVENT SHALL THE\nAUTHORS OR COPYRIGHT HOLDERS BE LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM, DAMAGES OR OTHER\nLIABILITY, WHETHER IN AN ACTION OF CONTRACT, TORT OR OTHERWISE, ARISING FROM,\nOUT OF OR IN CONNECTION WITH THE SOFTWARE OR THE USE OR OTHER DEALINGS IN THE\nSOFTWARE.","ref":"license.html"}],"proglang":"erlang","producer":{"name":"ex_doc","version":"0.39.1"},"content_type":"text/markdown"}